title: Hour 2: Who Is The New Mexico Coach?
description:
Spencer Hall of the Shutdown Fullcast (available in the LAF Network) brings his unique college football expertise to discussing Tennessee's chances against Alabama, whether we can believe in USC or UCLA, and Keith Richards' drug use.
